## Mailing Checklist

Before sending your dispute:

- [ ] Keep copies of ALL documents you are sending
- [ ] Do NOT send original documents (copies only)
- [ ] Use certified mail with return receipt requested
- [ ] Record the certified mail tracking number(s)
- [ ] Note the date mailed

